# Privacy Policy / Datenschutzerklärung

## 1. Overview

This application respects your privacy.  
No personal data is collected for advertising, tracking, or analytics purposes.

---

## 2. Data Collection

This app does not collect, store, or process any personal data for profiling or marketing purposes.

No analytics tools, advertising SDKs, or tracking technologies are used.

---

## 3. Platform Services (Apple / Google)

The app is distributed via:

- Apple App Store
- Google Play Store

These platforms may process limited technical and account-related data (e.g. device information, purchase history) according to their own privacy policies.

The developer has no access to payment details such as credit card or banking information.

---

## 4. Payments

All purchases are handled exclusively by Apple or Google via their respective app stores.

The developer does not process or store any payment information.

---

## 5. Contact

If you contact the developer via email, the provided data (e.g. email address and message content) will only be used to respond to your inquiry.

No data is shared with third parties.

---

## 6. Legal Basis

Processing of email inquiries is based on Art. 6 (1) (b) GDPR (processing necessary for handling inquiries).

---

## 7. Data Retention

Email correspondence is stored only as long as necessary to handle the inquiry or as required by law.

---

## 8. Changes

This privacy policy may be updated if legal or technical changes require it.